About Me

TL;DR

Im a marine biologist and science communicator by training, but Im taking all of the data analysis, statistics, and mathematical modeling skills Ive learned (and continue to learn) and Im now applying them to new problems.

The Long Version

My natural curiosity, love of animals and the environment, and constant pursuit of knowledge led me into a marine biology and chemistry double major in college (BS/BA) and a Masters degree in Marine Sciences. That generally leads people to think that I was playing with animals all day.
